fake_survey_df

Source: R/survey_df.R
fake_survey_df.Rd

dataframe of fake survey data (generated in data-raw) to enable testing of functions for survey data.

Usage

fake_survey_df

Format

A data frame with three variables:

person_id

numeric id, 1001-1010

question_concept_id

one of the actual 81 survey question concept ids for the 81 questions in the Social Determinants of Health Survey

answer

one of the possible answers, randomly chosen, for this question_concept_id

answer_concept_id

one of the actual 81 survey answer concept ids for the 81 questions in the Social Determinants of Health Survey

For further details on the SDOH survey for NIH AllOfUs, see https://www.researchallofus.org/data-tools/survey-explorer/social-determinants-survey/
